    <item>
      <title>How to Start Van Life on a Budget</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/how-to-start-van-life-on-a-budget/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/how-to-start-van-life-on-a-budget/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Starting van life on a budget is mostly about sequencing. People overspend when they buy comfort upgrades before core systems.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Phase 1: Buy the Right Van&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;phase-1-buy-the-right-van&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#phase-1-buy-the-right-van&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A reliable used van with service history beats a newer van you cannot afford to maintain. Budget for an inspection and first-month repairs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Start Here</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/start-here/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/start-here/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Van Life Starter Checklist&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;van-life-starter-checklist&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#van-life-starter-checklist&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you are new, do these in order:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Choose a reliable van and reserve a maintenance buffer.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Build only essentials first: sleep, airflow, basic power, basic cooking.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pick a simple power path: portable station now or full DIY later.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Test your routine for 30 days before buying comfort upgrades.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Use reviews with real tradeoffs, not just feature lists.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Beginner Jump Links&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;beginner-jump-links&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#beginner-jump-links&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/how-to-start-van-life-on-a-budget/&#34; &gt;How to Start Van Life on a Budget&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/budget-van-electrical-simple-vs-diy/&#34; &gt;Budget Van Electrical: Simple vs DIY&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/portable-power-stations-vs-full-electrical-build/&#34; &gt;Portable Power Stations vs Full Electrical Build&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/ventilation-mistakes-new-van-lifers-make/&#34; &gt;Ventilation Mistakes New Van Lifers Make&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Best-Of Guides to Use Next&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;best-of-guides-to-use-next&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#best-of-guides-to-use-next&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-of/van-solar/&#34; &gt;Best Budget Solar for Van Life&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-of/power-stations-under-500/&#34; &gt;Portable Power Stations Under $500&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-of/van-internet/&#34; &gt;Best Internet Setup for Van Life&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-of/van-kitchen/&#34; &gt;Best Van Kitchen Gear on a Budget&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Gear Reviews by Product&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;gear-reviews-by-product&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#gear-reviews-by-product&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/gear/bluetti-elite-200-v2-power-station-review/&#34; &gt;Bluetti Elite 200 V2 Review&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/gear/maxxair-maxxfan-deluxe-7500k-review/&#34; &gt;MaxxAir MaxxFan Deluxe 7500 Review&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/gear/crl-t-vent-windows-for-promaster-review/&#34; &gt;CRL T-Vent Windows Review&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/gear/renogy-100w-slim-solar-panels-stealth-promaster-setup/&#34; &gt;Renogy 100W Slim Solar Review&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
      
